        <p style="text-align: justify;">
         Our range of quality wall stickers from Roommates will provide you with inspiration to decorate every room of your house: From Nursery wall stickers to children's wall stickers, living room wall stickers and even for the office. With a vast array of styles and themes, including traditional, country, modern, retro and seasonal wall stickers you are sure to find a quality Home wall sticker to suit your own style and budget. All our 'peel &amp; stick' wall stickers (also called wall decals) designs are made of high-quality thin vinyl and can be easily repositioned, removed and reused. Be different and daring and choose a wall sticker that will add visual appeal and re-energise a space to create a whole new dimension.
        </p>
